  – +2 shield AC vs. ranged
  – Immunity to Magic Missile
  Range: Personal
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: Self

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Shocking Grasp
@60027 = ~Wand of Shocking Grasp~
@60028 = ~When activated, the wand electrically charges the wielder's hands; this charge will deal 1d2 fist damage and 1d8+%magnitude% points of electrical damage to a targeted creature. <PRO_HESHE> has 1 round per level to touch the target creature; if the wielder misses, the spell is wasted.

