  Damage:
  – 1d2 fist damage
  – 1d8+%magnitude% points of electrical damage
  Range: Touch
  Duration: Instant
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Sleep
@60029 = ~Wand of Sleep~
@60030 = ~This wand will emit a gold beam of energy at its targets up to a maximum range of 60 ft., affecting a 15-ft. radius. If the target creatures fail their Save vs. Death (with -3 penalty), they will fall into a deep, comatose sleep for %duration%. Monsters with 5 Hit Dice or more are unaffected. Attacks against sleeping opponents never miss.

STATISTICS:
(Enchantment/Charm)

Charge abilities:
– Sleep
  – Causes creatures in affected area to fall asleep
  Range: 60 ft.
  Duration: %duration%
  Area of Effect: 15-ft. radius
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Death (-3 penalty) negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Chill Touch
@60031 = ~Wand of Chill Touch~
@60032 = ~When activated, a blue glow encompasses the wielder's hand, and <PRO_HESHE> uses this energy to attack the life force of an adjacent creature. The creature is punched for 1d2 fist damage (Strength bonuses apply) and must make a Saving Throw vs. Wand or suffer 1d8 points of cold damage and receive a -2 THAC0 penalty for 5 rounds. Nonliving creatures such as golems and undead are unaffected by this spell.

STATISTICS:
(Necromancy)

Charge abilities:
– Chill Touch
