  – -2 penalty to THAC0 to target for 5 rounds
  Damage:
    – 1d2 fist
    – 1d8 cold damage
  Range: Touch
  Duration: 1 turn
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Saving Throw: Save vs. Wand negates panic (if undead)

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


